query_1_sql: SELECT location, COUNT(*) AS transaction_count FROM transactions WHERE user_id = 'U005' GROUP BY location ORDER BY transaction_count DESC;
query_2_sql: SELECT t.transaction_id, t.timestamp, t.amount, t.location FROM transactions t JOIN alerts a ON t.transaction_id = a.transaction_id WHERE a.user_id = 'U005' AND a.alert_type = 'GeoMismatch' ORDER BY t.timestamp DESC;
query_3_sql: SELECT la.ip_address, COUNT(*) AS login_attempts FROM login_attempts la WHERE la.user_id = 'U005' AND la.status = 'SUCCESS' GROUP BY la.ip_address ORDER BY login_attempts DESC;
query_4_sql: SELECT t.device_id, d.device_type, d.os, COUNT(*) AS transaction_count FROM transactions t JOIN devices d ON t.device_id = d.device_id WHERE t.user_id = 'U005' GROUP BY t.device_id, d.device_type, d.os ORDER BY transaction_count DESC;
query_5_sql: SELECT t.transaction_id, t.timestamp, t.amount, t.location FROM transactions t WHERE t.user_id = 'U005' AND t.location != (SELECT registered_location FROM users WHERE user_id = 'U005') ORDER BY t.timestamp DESC;
query_6_sql: SELECT DISTINCT location FROM transactions WHERE user_id = 'U005' AND timestamp > datetime('now', '-30 days')
query_8_sql: SELECT * FROM transactions WHERE user_id = 'U005' ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
query_9_sql: SELECT * FROM login_attempts WHERE user_id = 'U005' ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
query_11_sql: SELECT d.* FROM devices d JOIN user_devices ud ON d.device_id = ud.device_id WHERE ud.user_id = 'U005';
